Problem Definition.

--Create Scooter hiring system
-Electric scooters need to be charged at scooter charging station
-Users can only hire and unplug scooter IF battery charged
-Users ALWAYS use up baterry charger, battery will be empty after scooter used
-Takes 2000ms to charge scooter(asynchronuous)
oCreate async function setTimeout and setInterval(call back on next tick or when timer expires)


Class Scooter{
    Constructor(name)
    string type, color, name
    int speed
    int battery
    
    create() - calls array all scooter, adds a new scooter
    void repair()
    void check()
}

Class chargingStation{
    []allScooter

    constructor(location)
    string location

    method(charge) - charges scooter
    method(hire) - checks if scooter charged, then hire
    method(dBag) void method

}

class User{
    Constructor (age, account, name) - check if over 18 and has over 5 in account
    int age
    int account
    string name             
    void balance - charge
}




